com.google.android.exoplayer.chunk

Class Chunk

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer.chunk.Chunk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Loader.Loadable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MediaChunk

    public abstract class Chunk
extends java.lang.Object
implements Loader.Loadable
    An abstract base class for Loader.Loadable implementations that load chunks of data required for the playback of streams.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Chunk

        public Chunk(DataSource dataSource,
     DataSpec dataSpec,
     Format format,
     int trigger)
        Parameters:
        dataSource - The source from which the data should be loaded.
        dataSpec - Defines the data to be loaded. dataSpec.length must not exceed Integer.MAX_VALUE. If dataSpec.length == C.LENGTH_UNBOUNDED then the length resolved by dataSource.open(dataSpec) must not exceed Integer.MAX_VALUE.
        format - See format.
        trigger - See trigger.

        public final byte[] getLoadedData()
